summary: This is simply a save as a male Nord Prisoner in the Abandoned Prison from AS-LAL.
descriptionHtml:
This is simply a save as a male Nord Prisoner in the Abandoned Prison from AS-LAL.

Only SKSE, SkyUI, and Alternate Start - Live Another Life are installed.

Simply load in, open the console, and use the showracemenu command to customize your character.

This is being uploaded JUST in case you wanted a clean save, but also wanted to use Live Another Life.
author: Jester Blackguarde
